<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>新鲜的十二个有趣的笑话。来自俄罗斯的笑话。</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/</link><description>来自俄罗斯的轶事是最有趣的笑话，故事，格言和短语，诗歌，漫画和其他幽默。他们于1995年11月8日发布。由Dima Werner编译</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>轶事＃1 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511861</link><description>女士：&lt;br /&gt; - 明天已经是3月8日，但我还没有弄清楚我丈夫想给我什么！</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511861</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃2 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511862</link><description>- 当丈夫给她们自己赠送礼物时，女人不喜欢它。例如，沙发姨妈真的很喜欢...&lt;br /&gt; - 她的丈夫是谁？&lt;br /&gt; - 同样... de bears的通常强盗...</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511862</guid></item><item><title>07 Martha 2025的Anecdot＃3</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511863</link><description>- 亲爱的，好吧，你为什么这样做？&lt;br /&gt; - 我还很年轻...&lt;br /&gt; - 是两天前。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511863</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃4 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511864</link><description>德国厄休拉·冯·莱恩（Ursula von der Layen）提议支持Zelensky并将乌克兰变成“钢铁猪”。从字面上看，德语 - “ Sttyelshwan”或“幸存的猪”……厄休拉教导了特朗普学会羞辱的地方！</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511864</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃5 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511865</link><description>以前，人们有电话，现在手机有人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511865</guid></item><item><title>anecdot＃6 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511866</link><description>正如他们在欧盟中所说的，就像喉咙里的匈牙利一样！</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511866</guid></item><item><title>anecdot＃7 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511867</link><description>- 唐尼，如果下次Zelensky到达西装时，您会原谅他吗？&lt;br /&gt; - 只有穿着小丑服装！</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511867</guid></item><item><title>07 Martha 2025的轶事＃8</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511868</link><description>- 我不喜欢撒谎。&lt;br /&gt; - 你已经在撒谎了。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511868</guid></item><item><title>07 Martha 2025的anecdot＃9</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511869</link><description>昨晚我回家，几个聪明的醉汉问我最近的红色和白色商店。长期以来，这真是可惜，因为我不知道这一点，也没有帮助人们，其次，因为我看起来我应该知道这个地方。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511869</guid></item><item><title>轶事＃10 for 07 Martha 2025</title><link>https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511870</link><description>在一个克服儿童的糖果家族中，他们没有戈尔基。</description><pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.anekdot.ru/release/anekdot/day/2025-03-07/#1511870</guid></item></channel></rss>